#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:1
msgid "Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1"
msgstr "Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:5
msgid ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 is a state-of-the-art mixture-of-experts (MoE)"
" language model developed by Mistral AI. It features 8 expert models, "
"each with 7B parameters, and is specifically fine-tuned for instruction "
"following tasks."
msgstr ""
"Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 是由 Mistral AI 开发的最先进的混合专家（MoE）语言模型。"
"该模型包含8个专家模型，每个专家模型拥有7B参数，并专门针对指令跟随任务进行了微调。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:7
msgid "Key features of Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 include:"
msgstr "Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1 的主要特性包括："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:9
msgid ""
"8x7B parameters with sparse activation (only 2 experts activated per "
"token)"
msgstr "8x7B参数，采用稀疏激活（每个token仅激活2个专家）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:10
msgid "Strong performance across various NLP tasks"
msgstr "在各种NLP任务上表现优异"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:11
msgid "Support for extended context length"
msgstr "支持扩展上下文长度"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:12
msgid "High-quality instruction following capabilities"
msgstr "高质量的指令跟随能力"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:14
msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, "
"including supported features, feature configuration, environment "
"preparation, single-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点部署、精度和性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:16
msgid "The `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` model is supported in vllm-ascend."
msgstr "vllm-ascend 支持 `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` 模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:18
msgid "Environment Preparation"
msgstr "环境准备"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:20
msgid "Model Weight"
msgstr "模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:22
msgid ""
"`Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`(BF16 version): [Download model "
"weight](https://huggingface.co/mistralai/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1)"
msgstr ""
"`Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`(BF16版本)：[下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/mistralai/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:23
msgid "Quantized versions may be available from third-party providers."
msgstr "量化版本可能由第三方提供商提供。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:25
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to a local directory, such"
" as `/data/models/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到本地目录，例如 `/data/models/`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:27
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:29
msgid ""
"You can use our official docker image to run `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`"
" directly."
msgstr "您可以使用我们的官方docker镜像直接运行 `Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:31
msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动docker镜像，请参考[使用docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-docker)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:65
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr "部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:67
msgid "Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "单节点部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:69
msgid ""
"`Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16)"
" or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)."
msgstr ""
"`Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1` 可部署在1台 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 或 1台 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) 上。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:71
msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:103
msgid "**Notice:** The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr "**注意：** 参数说明如下："

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:106
msgid ""
"Setting the environment variable `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` "
"enables balance scheduling. This may help increase output throughput and "
"reduce TPOT in v1 scheduler. However, TTFT may degrade in some scenarios."
msgstr ""
"设置环境变量 `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` 可启用均衡调度。这有助于提高输出吞吐量并降低v1调度器中的TPOT。但在某些场景下，TTFT可能会下降。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:107
msgid ""
"`--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length - that is, the sum"
" of input and output tokens for a single request. For testing purposes, a"
" value of `4096` is used here."
msgstr ""
"`--max-model-len` 指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出token总和。为测试目的，此处使用 `4096`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:108
msgid ""
"`--dtype float16` specifies the data type for model weights and "
"computations."
msgstr "`--dtype float16` 指定模型权重和计算的数据类型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:109
msgid "`--trust-remote-code` allows loading models with custom code."
msgstr "`--trust-remote-code` 允许加载包含自定义代码的模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:110
msgid ""
"`--enforce-eager` forces the use of eager execution mode instead of graph"
" compilation, which can be more stable for some models."
msgstr ""
"`--enforce-eager` 强制使用即时执行模式而非图编译模式，这对某些模型可能更稳定。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:111
msgid ""
"`--block-size` specifies the block size for KV cache management, with a "
"value of `128` used here."
msgstr "`--block-size` 指定KV缓存管理的块大小，此处使用 `128`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1.md:112
msgid ""
"`--gpu-memory-utilization` sets the proportion of NPU memory to use for "
"the model, with a value of `0.7` used here to reduce memory usage."
msgstr "`--gpu-memory-utilization` 设置用于模型的NPU内存比例，此处使用 `0.7` 以减少内存使用。"

